_sText:
A Deathrun Map and its awesome!

trap 1: lasers (instant death)
trap 2: floor pushes you up against ceiling.
trap 3: wall pushes you from side, into endless (almost) hole
trap 4: teleports you to a room with fire
trap 5: fence (you need to climb over) with sparks (instant death)
trap 6: floor breaks (and you get teleportet to a Room on T-side, and T presses button = you fall in endless hole)
trap 7: spikes comes up from floor
trap 8: you get caught in a cage, and then walls from both sides pushes agains you (Tip: you can survive by jumping on top of the right wall)
trap 9 (Not a real trap) Floor breaks at the end, like a maze of breaking floors

- Then you get guns so you can kill the t's :D
